    <abstract>
    <t>0-RTT is designed to accelerate the throughput at the establishment of a connection. There are cases where 0-RTT alone does not improve the time to service. This memo proposes a solution where an additional parameter is registered during the 1-RTT phase to improve the initial throughput during subsequent 0-RTT.</t>
